.SH NAME
batadv_bla_purge_backbone_gw \- Remove backbone gateways after a timeout or immediately
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" batadv_bla_purge_backbone_gw
.BI "(struct batadv_priv *bat_priv "  ","
.BI "int now "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bat_priv" 12
the bat priv with all the soft interface information
.IP "now" 12
whether the whole hash shall be wiped now
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Check when we last heard from other nodes, and remove them in case of
a time out, or clean all backbone gws if now is set.
